{
  "stem": "1216.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And it was built in I think, the late 1780's.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But nothing changed between then and the time we got there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "In 1941, the Germans kicked out all the original inhabitants and sent in the first prisoners, essentially, to ready what became a concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It's often called a ghetto.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It wasn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And to ready it meant to put up bunk beds and, I suppose, subdivide rooms, and so on.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "What hadn't changed was the washrooms, which were much like Westerbork.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Any kind of hygienic appliances, they had been built, I suppose, to the latest standards in the 1780s, but by 1940 it was slightly different.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "The wash rooms did have faucets.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Very often they didn't work.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And you had to go and get water from the pump.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "The barracks were stone barracks built in a square with a courtyard in the middle.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And in the middle of that courtyard was a hand pump, in most barracks.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And that's where I remember getting our water.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "You went down with a pail, you pumped the water, and then you lugged your pail back up to where you lived.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And again, we had big rooms for about 50 people, I guess, then, with bunk beds, three high again, but now made of wood.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And that became important, eventually.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "There were some smaller rooms, probably originally officer's rooms, but now also shared.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "There was not ever, I think, one person per room.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Later, we had one of those small rooms, and we shared it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "There were five people, five of us in that room, which was meant for one person.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Theresienstadt had originally being built for 7,000 people, half soldiers and half civilians, roughly.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "By the time we got there, it held mostly 60,000 people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "So was a little overcrowded.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
